<p>A question that I would have for Ryan, which Jack, you did not ask, is if you think there is a place for a militia in the way that Jack (and the constitutions) defines it. If the answer is yes, then why, Ryan, are you trying to replace that with your system, by calling it a &#8220;Militia&#8221; when by definition, it is not. (Conversely, if you think there is no place for a traditional militia, I understand your motifs for attempting to re-brand the militia, although I would disagree with and oppose such actions).</p>
